x^n
x^n + y^n = [1 + m^n]^n + (m[1 + m^n])^n = [1 + m^n]^n + m^n \cdot [1 + m^n]^n  \\ = [1 + m^n] \cdot [1 + m^n]^n = [1 + m^n]^{n+1} = x^{n+1} = z^{n+1}
